front.title: •IG-88 In IG-2000
front.gametext: May add 2 passengers. Permanent pilot is •IG-88, who adds 2 to power and 3 to maneuver. May initiate battle. When in a battle you initiate, adds one battle destiny. Ion Cannon may deploy aboard.
front.lore: Starship adapted to the assassin droid's specifications. Flight controls linked directly to processing unit. Real-time relays minimize response time.
